author: Seattle Times staff
title: Thursday’s prep tennis results
text:
Charles Wright Academy 5, Cascade Christian 0 Singles —1, Griffin Welsh, CW, beat David Jennings, CC, 6-0, 6-1; 2, Wyatt Iverson, CWA, beat Trevor Wissing, CC, 6-1, 6-2. 
Doubles —1, Raghav Agrawal-Micah Wibowo, CWA, beat Jack Hannah-Taylor Backus, CC, 6-3, 6-0; 2, Jack Jorgenson-Jasper Xin, CWA, beat Nick Petrescu-Ryan Mowreader, CC, 6-2, 6-1; 3, Karl Bulley-Cole Harrington, CWA, beat Conner Davidson-Danny DeBock, CC, 6-3, 6-2.
